Definition: showing characteristics of age, especially having grey or white hair
Example: whose beard with age is hoar-Coleridge; nodded his hoary head
Synonyms: gray, grey-haired, gray-haired, grey-headed, gray-headed, grizzly, noun, artifact, grizzle, hoar, hoary, attribute, hoariness, white-haired, showing, characteristics, of, age, especially, having, or, white, hair, whose, beard, with, is, -Coleridge, nodded, his, head
Category: adj.all
